{
  "stem": "5516.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They got uniforms, and they got-- they're nice looking, too, the German girls.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] They put the kids on buses, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when he say, the commandant-- the SS commandant, he was running this-- he say, you cannot take care of the kids in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We will take them in a place where they will have good, supervised, you know, and good food, and clothes, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because it's no good for kids to-- The president from the ghetto-- I forgot his name.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], I think.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I forgot his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "His son survived, I think, and he's now in Israel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then he say, I know where you take them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then he say, if you don't believe us, we will take him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You go with him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And after this, you will come in back and you will tell the ghetto members, your people, where you left them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I wait-- still I'm waiting, now, to see him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Never.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Never.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Never.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a lot of stories what happened, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even these SS men, and the police chief from the Lithuanian police.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had a doctor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He's now in New York.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When after the war, he was a doctor for the United Nations, for the Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They made a special hospital for the survivors, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was the doctor in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In the ghetto, they have a little place, like two by four.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And some bad cases, they used to take in for a few days, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So one time, a lady ran away from a place where they kill the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Not even from Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She was going place by place, till she find out it's a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she was in the ghetto-- the Siauliai ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Until they find out.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
